document.topic_text: old pictures of natacha peyre, elena belle with family friends, miss lopez, elena belle English/ Today looking to pictures at home with my family. Look what I have found?. In the middle me with children in Sweden some years ago. At that time I had my two daughters with me and I used to meet some friends children too. To the right with dark hair, my Spanish friends Angela daughter, Natacha Peyre, now Elena Belle. Now she looks very different…… Svenska/ Idag hemma kollade vi tillsammans med gamla bilder med familjen. Kolla på vad jag har hittat!. Jag i mitten och min kompis barn till höger Natacha Peyre, nu ">Elena Belle och ser väldigt annorlunda…
